[GameId "2127765595566628"]

{We come to the difficult question of our [b1]-knight. While the king's knight will go to [f3] with no exceptions (as far as I can tell each of the 1000 or so variations in this course has [Nf3]) , our queen's knight has a bit more variety.} 1. Nc3 $1 {[%csl Rc5][%cal Gc3a4] Against the [c5]/[c6]-pawn scramble, we invariably aim for [a4] via [c3] to target the [c5]-weakness.} *

