ier.} 11. Na4 dxe3 {This has never been played thus far, but it seems half logical. A trade would weaken the appearance of White's king.} 12. dxe3 {Appearances can be deceiving and Black doesn't have anything. We can always take back on [d1] with the rook to keep castling privileges.} Ne4 (12... Qa5+ 13. Bc3 {and the checks end early.}) 13. O-O $14 {Sooner or later, the queens will be traded and Black will be left with an ugly structure.} *

