 a benefit; [f6] is now a weakness for eternity, frozen in space while [f5] obstructs its path.} (10... Qf7 $2 {drops a pawn to} 11. Qxf5 {.}) 11. Qf3 $14 {[%cal Gb1c3,Ge1c1] We will play [Nc3] and [O-O-O]. The computer calls it slightly better, but it seems practically so much easier to play. Black will struggle to even figure out where to place the king safely.} *

