queenside.} a5 8. b5 $13 {[%cal Gc1b2,Gf1e2] We keep things closed for the time being. We can aim for [Bb2] and [Be2]; [d2]-[d4] could also be played, but then it would be better to keep the bishop on [c1], such that it can head to [d2], keeping the [e3]-weakness under control.} *

