he pressure.} Bg4 {Black's last chance to get this move in.} 10. h3 {We will reluctantly claim the bishop pair.} Bxf3 11. Qxf3 $16 {[%cal Gb1c3,Gc1d2,Ga1e1] Our space advantage continues to impress. We will play [Nc3], [Bd2], and [Rae1]. We are waiting for the perfect moment to break through with [e4]-[e5], but there is no rush!} *

