 anchored to the [f4]-pawn it can scan the board from its central perch.} Ba6 {This move never works, but that won't stop your opponent from trying it.} 12. c4 {[%csl Ra6,Gb3,Gc4,Gd3][%cal Gd2d3] Followed by [d2]-[d3], when [c4] will be made concrete and the [a6]-bishop will be granted the position of an irrelevant clown.} *

