k! Snatching the pawn would ruin our structure so we have to budge and allow Black to trade off one of the bad pawns.} 13. Ne5 cxb3 {How should we recapture?} 14. cxb3 $16 {[%csl Rc6][%cal Ga1c1,Gc1c8] That's where the good news for Black ends. The [c6]-pawn has been rendered even weaker, as White's c-file is now open. Black has a difficult middlegame and endgame ahead of them.} *

