rce [c4] and place the bishop on [d2]. We don't need to rush, as we have a firm grip on the center. If Black plays ...[d6]-[d5], we will respond with [e4]-[e5], and if they go for ...[e6]-[e5], we can respond with [f4]-[f5].} *

