e [d5]-apple.} e6 7. Bd3 Nf6 8. O-O Bxc5 9. Kh1 $14 {[%cal Gd1e1,Ge3e4,Ga2a3,Gb2b4] Sidestepping the pin on the [e3]-pawn. White has a healthy edge. We can start with [a2]-[a3], introducing annoying ideas of [b2]-[b4]. Then we can follow with [Qe1] and [e3]-[e4] ideas to liberate our entombed [c1]-bishop.} *

