Lines will open! Our knight hopes to enter the weak [d6]-square in the not-so-distant future.} cxd4 13. Qf2 $16 {[%csl Rd4][%cal Gf3d4] White will capture on [d4], when Black will be playing a game of catch-up with their undeveloped pieces. Importantly, Black can't reinforce the pawn with ...[Ne7]-[f5] since that would weaken the [c6]-knight and we could respond with [Bb5].} *

