5 {That's wizard's chess, Harry.} Nc7 11. hxg6 hxg6 (11... fxg6 {keeps the h-file closed but weakens the diagonal gravely:} 12. Bc4+ e6 13. Ng5 {+- . Ouch!}) 12. Qe2 $18 {[%cal Ge2f2,Gf2h4] The queen is on its way to the h-file, either via [f2] to [h4], or to [h2] after the 2nd rank has been cleared by [g2]-[g4]. White will crash through with a winning attack.} *

