een is short of squares.} Qd5 {loses to} 21. Nf6+ {discovery tricks.}) 20... Qd7 21. Nc5 {[%cal Gc5e6] We will snatch the nice bishop on [e6] and then crash through on [b7]. Black's structure is shattered and will quickly lose a second pawn, evening out the material. The bishop pair and our activity already give us a winning advantage according to the silicon dragon.} *

